== 制作 ==
2017年3月，[[天空之舞传媒|天空之舞传媒]]购得漫画书《永生守卫》的电影改编权<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/skydance-picks-up-rights-greg-rucka-comic-old-guard-990567/|title=Skydance Picks Up Rights to Greg Rucka Comic 'Old Guard' (Exclusive)|date=2017-03-31|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|access-date=2017-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401041049/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/skydance-picks-up-rights-greg-rucka-comic-old-guard-990567|archive-date=2017-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月，他们聘请[[吉娜·普林斯-拜斯伍德|吉娜·普林斯-拜斯伍德]]出任导演，原作者鲁卡担任編劇，天空之舞的[[大卫·埃里森|大卫·埃里森]]、达娜·戈德堡和{{tsl|en|Don Granger|唐·格兰杰}}出任制片人<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/gina-prince-blythewood-directing-skydance-the-old-guard-1202884404/|title=Gina Prince-Bythewood to Direct 'The Old Guard' for Skydance|date=2018-07-25|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2018-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725221745/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/gina-prince-blythewood-directing-skydance-the-old-guard-1202884404/|archive-date=2018-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凭借着7000万美元的预算，吉娜成为首位执导漫画改编大片的黑人女导演<ref name=DeadlineBudget/>。2019年3月，Netflix与天空之舞达成融资协议，正式购下影片全球发行权。随后，查理兹·塞隆加入剧组，同时与AJ·迪克斯、 贝丝·科诺及马克·埃文斯加入制片人行列<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/charlize-theron-netflix-the-old-guard-movie-1202561033/|title=Charlize Theron & KiKi Layne Comic Book Action Feature ‘The Old Guard’ Lands At Netflix|date=2019-02-21|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030135142/https://deadline.com/2019/02/charlize-theron-netflix-the-old-guard-movie-1202561033/|archive-date=2019-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Netflix买下版权后，琪琪·兰恩确认加入剧组。2019年5月，馬文·坎薩林、馬提亞斯·修奈爾和{{tsl|en|Luca Marinelli|卢卡·马里内利}}加入剧组<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/aladdins-jafar-marwan-kenzari-joins-charlize-theron-old-guard-1214007|title=Jafar Actor Marwan Kenzari Joins Charlize Theron in Action Thriller 'Old Guard' (Exclusive)|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=2019-05-28|accessdate=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528213229/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/aladdins-jafar-marwan-kenzari-joins-charlize-theron-old-guard-1214007|archive-date=2019-05-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/matthias-schoenaerts-luca-marinelli-star-action-thriller-old-guard-1214761|title=Matthias Schoenaerts, Luca Marinelli Board Charlize Theron Action Thriller 'The Old Guard'|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=2019-05-31|accessdate=2019-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531132907/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/matthias-schoenaerts-luca-marinelli-star-action-thriller-old-guard-1214761|archive-date=2019-05-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年6月，哈利·米尔林、吴青芸和切瓦特·艾乔福加入剧组<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/the-old-guard-chiwetel-ejiofor-harry-melling-veronica-ngo-join-netflix-skydance-medias-action-fantasy-1202636108/|title=‘The Old Guard’: Chiwetel Ejiofor, Harry Melling & Veronica Ngo Join Netflix & Skydance Media’s Action-Fantasy|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Andreas|last=Wiseman|date=2019-06-21|accessdate=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621135120/https://deadline.com/2019/06/the-old-guard-chiwetel-ejiofor-harry-melling-veronica-ngo-join-netflix-skydance-medias-action-fantasy-1202636108/|archive-date=2019-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。应个人请求，吴青芸的角色较原著漫画有所改动。在采访中，鲁卡表示：“维罗妮卡一角上线时，她就说我不是日本人，我是越南人。（导演）找到我，说‘我们可能接纳这点吗？’，我就说‘当然可以’......范子变成了奎恩，奎恩现在就是越南人。它真的很简单，只要你所做并尊重它”<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Polo|first=Susana|date=July 10, 2020|title=Netflix’s Old Guard ends with setup for a devastating sequel, says the comic’s creator|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/7/10/21317953/netflix-the-old-guard-charlize-theron-quinn-sequel-final-scene-credits-scene-comic-origins|access-date=2020-07-13|website=Polygon|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712214410/https://www.polygon.com/2020/7/10/21317953/netflix-the-old-guard-charlize-theron-quinn-sequel-final-scene-credits-scene-comic-origins|archive-date=2020-07-12}}</ref>。角色的死亡也有所变更：“漫画书中，范子/奎恩是被暴风雨冲出船的，而不是立马被淹死。按照鲁卡的说法，这是部分出于节省资金而做出的逻辑变更......但奎恩的新‘死法’是被导演铁娘子形象的建议而固化了，扮演着重要的叙事和定调角色”<ref name=":0" />。

