==发行==
影片于2020年7月10日上线Netflix<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/05/first-look-at-charlize-theron-immortal-warrior-in-the-old-guard|title=First Look at Charlize Theron’s Immortal Warrior in The Old Guard|website=Vanity Fair|first=Anthony|last=Breznican|date=2020-05-07|accessdate=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612230535/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/05/first-look-at-charlize-theron-immortal-warrior-in-the-old-guard|archive-date=2020-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在首周末成为该网站点播量最高流媒体节目<ref>{{Cite web |title= Weekend Box Office: The Most-Watched Movies At Home (And In Drive-In Theaters) Over The Weekend |url= https://uproxx.com/movies/empire-strikes-back-old-guard-box-office-outpost/ |last= Rowles |first= Dustin |website= Uproxx |date= 2020-07-12 |access-date= 2020-07-12 |archive-date= 2020-07-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200712180950/https://uproxx.com/movies/empire-strikes-back-old-guard-box-office-outpost/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。另据7月17日的报道，Netflix表示影片首月观看用户数有望达到7200万，是该平台10大最成功作品之一<ref name=D'Alessandro-July2020>{{Cite web |title= Charlize Theron Netflix Movie ‘The Old Guard’ Heading To 72M Households To Rank Among Streamer’s 10 Most Popular Pics |url= https://deadline.com/2020/07/charlize-theron-netflix-movie-the-old-guard-record-viewership-top-10-netflix-movies-1202988858/ |last= D'Alessandro |first= Anthony |website= Deadline Hollywood |date= 2020-07-17 |access-date= 2020-07-18 |archive-date= 2020-12-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201225234133/https://deadline.com/2020/07/charlize-theron-netflix-movie-the-old-guard-record-viewership-top-10-netflix-movies-1202988858/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

为宣传影片的发行，Netflix于7月17日到19日举行一场俯视角[[清版动作游戏|清版动作]][[网页游戏|网页游戏]]比赛，承诺会在活动结束后向积分最高者提供长达83年的Netflix“永久”免费订阅权<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moon |first1=Mariella |title=Netflix's 'Old Guard' video game contest promises an 83-year subscription |url=https://www.engadget.com/netflix-old-guard-video-game-contest-075037460.html |website=Engadget |accessdate=2020-07-19 |date=2020-07-17 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129083010/https://www.engadget.com/netflix-old-guard-video-game-contest-075037460.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==评价==
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据147条评论，给影片打出80%的新鲜度，平均分6.54/10。网站共识写道：“《永生守卫》有时会受到超级英雄片之间约定俗成的规矩给拘束住，但导演吉娜·普林斯-拜斯伍德给这个流派带来了更复杂的视野，以及由查理兹·塞隆主导的杰出动作戏<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_old_guard|title=The Old Guard (2020)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Fandango Media|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301050617/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_old_guard|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据41条评论打出平均分70/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web|title=The Old Guard Reviews|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-old-guard|website=Metacritic|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711193300/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-old-guard|archive-date=2020-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《{{le|独立连线|IndieWire}}》的凯特·埃布兰（{{lang|en|Kate Erbland}}）打出“B+”的评价，认为“影片深陷于拳拳到肉的动作戏......但用了足量的枪战戏点燃一场小规模内斗，每场动作戏不仅令人敬畏，而且对影片本身也至关重要。超级英雄的战斗无疑令人瞠目结舌，助推剧情发展”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Erbland|first1=Kate|title=‘The Old Guard’ Review: Gina Prince-Bythewood Delivers Netflix’s Best 2020 Action Movie|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/the-old-guard-review-gina-prince-bythewood-netflix-1234570629/|accessdate=2020-07-11|work=IndieWire|date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708073234/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/the-old-guard-review-gina-prince-bythewood-netflix-1234570629/|archive-date=2020-07-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的{{tsl|en|Owen Gleiberman|欧文·格里伯曼}}认为影片是一部“备受瞩目、值得观看的改编作品”，认为：“影片的许多场景很宏大、公式化（纠缠了两个小时），但导演吉娜·普林斯-拜斯伍德（在《{{le|爱情和篮球|Love & Basketball}}》和《{{le|蜜蜂的秘密生活|The Secret Life of Bees}}》之后作出了大转变）用成熟的执行技巧策划战斗场面，在演出阵容中挑逗某种深入灵魂的品质<ref>{{cite web |date= 2020-07-03 |last= Gleiberman |first= Owen |title= Charlize Theron in ‘The Old Guard’ on Netflix: Film Review |url= https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/the-old-guard-review-charlize-theron-chiwetel-ejiofor-1234697693/ |website= Variety |access-date= 2020-07-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200708060637/https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/the-old-guard-review-charlize-theron-chiwetel-ejiofor-1234697693/ |archive-date= 2020-07-08 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”

片中对超级英雄同性恋特征的描绘也获得赞赏。《[[每日野兽|每日野兽]]》的凯文·法伦（{{lang|en|Kevin Fallon}}）认为影片是首部超级英雄[[出柜|出柜]]的电影，或者说是有酷儿角色并承认她们之间爱情的罕见动作电影：“角色们的性别实际上与他们打坏人的能力毫无关联，反而还展现出表达她们的爱的尊严<ref>{{Cite news|last=Fallon|first=Kevin|date=2020-07-13|title=‘The Old Guard’ Finally Gives Us Gay Superheroes|language=en|work=The Daily Beast|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/netflixs-the-old-guard-finally-gives-us-gay-superheroes-and-its-more-beautiful-than-we-hoped|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713212142/https://www.thedailybeast.com/netflixs-the-old-guard-finally-gives-us-gay-superheroes-and-its-more-beautiful-than-we-hoped|archive-date=2020-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[卫报|卫报]]》的本杰明·李（{{lang|en|Benjamin Lee}}）写道：“在2020年，这真的不是什么大事，但看到一部面向大众的电影在奇幻漫画改编框架范围中，展示酷儿间不受拘束的爱，在我看来很重要<ref>{{Cite news|last=Lee|first=Benjamin|date=2020-07-10|title=Finally, a major Hollywood franchise movie with a gay romance|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jul/10/the-old-guard-charlize-theron-gay-romance|access-date=2020-07-13|issn=0261-3077|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713070420/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jul/10/the-old-guard-charlize-theron-gay-romance|archive-date=2020-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[纽约时报|Decider]]的安娜·蒙塔（{{lang|en|Anna Menta}}）说自己没有读过《永生守卫》的漫画，不知道编剧格雷格·鲁卡的合同有没有规定影片无论怎么都应该包括出轨场景。所以当这一幕出现时，仍会让人觉得这是疯狂的举动，如同{{le|索罗家族|Solo family|韩和莱娅}}、[[蜘蛛侠|彼得和MJ]]、[[饥饿游戏三部曲|皮塔和凯妮丝]]以及其他在近几年的动作片中深情吻对方的异性恋情侣一样，很激情、很带电、很打动人<ref>{{Cite web|last=Menta|first=Anna|date=2020-07-13|title=‘The Old Guard’ Kiss Is The LGBT Representation Action Movies Need|url=https://decider.com/2020/07/13/the-old-guard-joe-nicky-kiss-netflix/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714010953/https://decider.com/2020/07/13/the-old-guard-joe-nicky-kiss-netflix/|archive-date=2020-07-14|access-date=2020-07-13|website=Decider|language=en-US}}</ref>。

